sequenceDiagram
  participant Merchant
  participant Wallet
  participant Issuer
  participant Gateway
  participant Backend

  Merchant->>Wallet: Handshake request
  Note right of Merchant: {merchantId, scope, endpoint,<br/>ttlMs, nonce}

  Wallet->>Wallet: User reviews request

  alt User approves
    Wallet->>Issuer: Approval confirmation
    Issuer-->>Merchant: Visa token
    Note right of Issuer: signed {iss, sub, merchantId,<br/>aud, scope, endpoint,<br/>nonce, iat, exp, kid}
  else User rejects
    Wallet-->>Merchant: REJECT — no token issued
  end

  Merchant->>Gateway: Request + visa token
  Gateway->>Gateway: Verify token
  Note right of Gateway: signature · exp · nonce<br/>merchantId · endpoint · aud

  alt Token valid
    Gateway->>Backend: Forward verified request
  else Token invalid
    Gateway-->>Merchant: 401 Unauthorized
  end